課程概述 Course Description
       Master basic electromagnetism by "solving" standard (senior to graduate level) E&M problems. Be capable of handling Maxwell's equation.Master basic electromagnetism by "solving" standard (senior to graduate level) E&M problems. Be capable of handling Maxwell's equation.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
Revisit electrodynamics by solving paradigmatic EM problems. Establish grounds to understand collective particle behavior in EM fields.Understand how EM theories constitute the basis of modern technology. 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Vector Analysis, Maxwell equations2Wave basics and Fourier analysis3Maxwell equations revisited4Maxwell equations revisited5Electrostatics 6Electrostatics 7Electrostatics 8Electromagnetism and its relation to relativity9Electromagnetism and its relation to relativity10Charged particle dynamics11Magnetostatics12Magnetostatics13Magnetostatics14Time variation of electromagnetic field15Time variation of electromagnetic field16Retarted potentials and radiation17Introduction to Laser Physics18Introduction to Laser Physics 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


